cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.ET, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for automatic design of analog circuits using deep learning, which involves generating a chain of circuit components and predicting their parameters. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of a hypernetwork scheme and a differential simulator also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY) and electronic devices and circuits (cs.ET). Finally, the paper's focus on designing efficient solutions suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
